import React from 'react' import './verification.css' const Verification = ({userEmail}) => { return (

Please verify your email

We sent a verification email to {userEmail} . Please click on the link to activate your account.

If you don't see an email, please make sure the above email is correct and check your spam folder.

Click here to resend email verification email or change your email.

) } export default Verification
